es.situm.sdk.v1

Class SitumDataManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • es.situm.sdk.v1.SitumDataManager
  • Deprecated. 
    use CommunicationManager from SitumSdk.communicationManager() instead

    @Deprecated
public final class SitumDataManager
extends java.lang.Object
    Access to Situm Indoor Maps data. This class is thread safe. Fetchings are done in a background thread. The callbacks are called in the Main thread.
